<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śakāptam</hi> Āyirattu munnūṟṟu nāliṉ mel cellāniṉṟa <hi rend="grantha">dundubhi</hi> varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣam <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> ya3</hi> tiyati canikkiḻamaiyum <hi rend="grantha">paurnam</hi> Aiyum peṟṟa tiruvātirai nāḷ <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭacoḻamaṇṭalattu
<lb n="2"/>Āṟṟūrnāṭṭut tirukkāḷatti Āṉa mummuṭicoḻapurattu nāyaṉār tirukkāḷatti<unclear>uṭaiya nā</unclear>yaṉārkku <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>ma<hi rend="grantha">nma hāmaṇḍa</hi> le<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi> ra Arirāyavi<hi rend="grantha">bhāḷa bhā ṣai</hi>kkuttappuva rāyarakaṇṭa <hi rend="grantha">mahi</hi>ta<hi rend="grantha">la</hi> pati <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> <unclear>yirattu mu</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>veṇu<hi rend="grantha">bhā</hi>vā A<hi rend="grantha">jā</hi>vaṇa<hi rend="grantha">jā</hi>ni <hi rend="grantha">puṇya</hi>vaṇi<hi rend="grantha">jā <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> </hi> vā<hi rend="grantha">ha</hi>na<hi rend="grantha"> gajasiṅga gaṇḍapeṇḍārūpa</hi> vaṇṭā<hi rend="grantha">rāca ji</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">rakṣa śaṅgemāsama</hi>tta r <hi rend="grantha">ke</hi> s- <hi rend="grantha">koṇḍamisa <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> vīramaṇḍaḷi</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">kurā</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha">mīsarakaṇḍa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kaḷāmaṇḍaḷiśara <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> </hi> lā<hi rend="grantha">ḷarā</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha">bha</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha">ṅkara</hi> O<hi rend="grantha">śaḷada ḷa</hi>vi<hi rend="grantha">bhāḷa baḷaka <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ci <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> mātyabhaṅga <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> </hi>
<lb n="5"/>vi<hi rend="grantha">bhā</hi> ḷa ciṅkalakkumārakaṇṭa <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vīramaracappauṭaiyār kumāra mallappauṭaiyar <unclear>tiruvātirai</unclear> ma<hi rend="grantha">hā</hi>pūcaikku veṇṭum Avaiyiṟṟukku melaippaṭṭaiyanāṭṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>koṭṭikkāṭṭil pātiyāl Uḷḷa kaṭamai poṉvariyum tukkaṇar kāṇikkai <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kāṇikkai Uḷḷiṭṭa kāṇikkaivakaiyum maṟṟum Epperppaṭṭa cakala Upāti
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kaḷum Uṭpaṭa <hi rend="grantha">sarvva</hi> māṉṉiyam Āka nāyaṉārkku tevatāṉam Āka ca<unclear>ntirātittavarai yum</unclear> celvatāka viṭṭeṉ Inta mutal koṇṭu Intat tiruvātirai <hi rend="grantha">mahā</hi> pūcaiyum ca<hi rend="grantha">ntrādi</hi> tta
<lb n="8" break="no"/>varaiyāka nammuṭaiya perāle naṭakkakkaṭavatākavum <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Inta ta<hi rend="grantha">rmma</hi> ttukku vi<hi rend="grantha">laṅ</hi> kam paṇṇiṉār Uṇṭākil keṅkaikkaraiyil kurālpacuvai koṉṟāṉ pā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>vattile pokakkaṭavāṉ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Itu paṉmā<hi rend="grantha">heśvara ra kṣai</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
